strings.Value: "This group is shaping up nicely! We just have to try a little harder tomorrow. If I wrote a true account of our battles, people with think we're a bunch of amateurs. Would it hurt to strike a heroic pose now and then, Regongar? You grump."
"Enough about your hero, Guy-what's-his-face, alright Linzi? It's just a story. No one can be that good. Only idiots and dead men flourish when they fight. Stop with the nonsense already!"
